      6. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">rostopic</code>: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">node</code>лҒјлҰ¬ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sub, pub</code>н•ҳлҠ” <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">topic</code>мқ„ мқҳлҜён•ңлӢӨ. мҳҲлҘј л“Өм–ҙ, н•ҳлӮҳмқҳ nodeлҠ” м—¬лҹ¬к°ңмқҳ nodeлЎң л¶Җн„° м—¬лҹ¬к°ңмқҳ topicмқ„ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sub</code> н•ҳкі  м•Ңкі лҰ¬мҰҳмқ„ мҲҳн–үн•ҳм—¬ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pub</code>н•ҳлҠ” нҳ•нғңлЎң м—¬лҹ¬ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">node</code>мҷҖ мқён„°нҺҳмқҙмӢұн•ҳкІҢ лҗңлӢӨ. мқҙ л•Ң, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">rostopic echo нҶ н”Ҫ</code>мқ„ нҶөн•ҙ ros м•Ҳм—җм„ң <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">node</code>к°„ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pub, sub</code>н•ҳлҠ” topicмқ„ н„°лҜёл„җ м°Ҫм—җм„ң ліј мҲҳ мһҲлӢӨ.<br />
