    <ul>
      <li>etc. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">rostopic list</code>: pub,sub лҗҳкі  мһҲлҠ” <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">topic</code>л“Өмқҳ listлҘј ліҙм—¬мӨҢ</li>
      <li>etc. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">rosnode list</code>: node info м•Ңл ӨмӨҢ</li>
      <li>etc. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">rostopic info xxxx</code>: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">xxxx</code>topicмқҳ informationмқ„ м•Ңл ӨмӨҢ. мҳҲлҘј л“Өл©ҙ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">Type: styx_msgs/Lane</code></li>
      <li>etc. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">rosmsg info styx_msgs/Lane</code>: <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">styx_msgs/Lane</code>мқҳ msg кө¬мЎ°лҘј м•Ңл ӨмӨҢ</li>
      <li>etc. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">rospy.loginfo</code> л“ұ лЎңк·ё л©”мӢңм§Җ <a href="http://wiki.ros.org/rospy_tutorials/Tutorials/Logging">ROS.org</a></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">node</code>лҘј кө¬лҸҷмӢңнӮӨлҠ” л°©мӢқ
      1. rate(x) мЈјкё° мһ‘лҸҷ
          - <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">rospy.rate(x)</code>лҘј мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҳм—¬ nodeк°Җ sampling rateлҘј к°Җм§Җкі  л°ҳліө мһ‘лҸҷн•ҳкІҢ н•ҳлҠ” л°©мӢқмңјлЎң, <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">rate.sleep()</code>кіј к°ҷмқҙ м“ҙлӢӨ. 
      2. spin() call back мһ‘лҸҷ
          - <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">rospy.spin()</code>мқҖ topicмқҙ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">subs</code>лҗҳл©ҙ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">callback</code>н•ЁмҲҳлҘј мқҙмҡ©н•ҳм—¬ nodeк°Җ мһ‘лҸҷлҗҳкІҢ н•ҳлҠ” л°©мӢқмқҙлӢӨ.
      - л‘җк°ңмқҳ л°©мӢқмқҖ н•ҳлӮҳмқҳ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">node</code>м—җм„ң к°ҷмқҙ мҚЁлҸ„ лҗңлӢӨ.
      3. мӮ¬мҡ© мҳҲмӢң</p>

    <div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>      ```python
      class ROS_NODE(object):
          def __init__(self):
              self.pub = rospy.Publisher('/mode', topic_msg, queue_size=1)

              # call_back н•ЁмҲҳ, subsк°Җ л“Өм–ҙмҷҖм•ј мһ‘лҸҷ
              rospy.Subscriber('/node', topic_msg, self.call_back)
              rospy.spin()

              # лҳҗлҠ” мЈјкё° н•ЁмҲҳ
              self.loop()
            
          def loop(self):
              rate = rospy.Rate(50)
              while not rospy.is_shutdown():
                  # м•Ңкі лҰ¬мҰҳ, мЈјкё°м ҒмңјлЎң мһ‘лҸҷ
                  publish()

                  rate.sleep()
            
          def publish(self):
              msg = topic_msg()
              self.pub.publish(msg)
      ```
</code></pre></div>    </div>
